13.0 Legal assistance
.br
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
Insurance sum payable: DKK 150,000 per person.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
13.1 Coverage
.br
The insurance provides for payment of deductible, if the insured has an
accident in a rented car, and lessor requires the insured to pay
deductible.
.sp 3mm
It is a condition of coverage that the damage was not caused by the insured
having acted with gross negligence or intentionally. See general exceptions
in section A, clause 5.0.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
